Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
Action This is a class designed to represent an Action done by a character
ActionManager The ActionManager Class is responsible for handling the keyInputs (and possibly later mouse inputs) and determining a proper response
Character This class is for a character on the level.
Consumables This class holds information regarding consumable(1 time use) items not implemented yet
Cursor Method to hold cursor information
Equipment Equipment is an equippable item not implemented yet
Game The class that holds both the frame and the canvas This class is responsible for maintaining and painting the window and implements the keyListener that forwards the events to an instance of the ActionManager class
Interactable Interactable is an extension of the PhysicalObject Class This is reserved for non character interactable objects i.e.
Item This class represents an in-game item and the data needed for it notr implemented yet
Job This class holds data for a characers job/class
Level This class stores the data needed for a level This includes a list of objects on the field, a grid of tiles, and a list of characters in their turn order.
LevelEditor Class being created to create a GUI Level Editor and write the level information into a file may have parts reworked to use in a save state function
moveTile Holds information regarding movement may want to consider making this an inner class
PhysicalObject Base Class for objects provides framework for derived classes pure PhysicalObjects are not interactable although they do occupy space on the level i.e.trees,walls, etc
StatusEffect StatusEffect is a class that stores data of a status effect on a character (poison, slow, buffs, etc) Not fully built yet
Tile Tile is a class that holds information for a specific tile in the level
